---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Mohan Rajendran — Senior SDE at Amazon, distributed systems and GenAI."
>
  <main>
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <article class="about-content">
      <p>
        I'm a Senior Software Development Engineer at Amazon, currently working at
        <strong>Amazon Photos</strong> on data pipelines, GenAI applications, and cloud
        migration initiatives.
      </p>
      <p>
        Previously, I was part of the founding team building infrastructure and data
        systems for Sponsored Products' Product Attribute Targeting — systems that handle
        high-volume traffic and serve millions of customers.
      </p>

      <h2>What I write about</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is where I think out loud. Most posts fall into one of these buckets:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Distributed systems</strong> — consistency models, consensus protocols, failure modes</li>
        <li><strong>AI/ML systems</strong> — inference, vector search, embedding pipelines, RAG</li>
        <li><strong>Computer science fundamentals</strong> — algorithms, data structures, SICP</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud infrastructure</strong> — AWS, data engineering, cost patterns</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        I believe in learning in public — documenting both the things that worked
        and the things that didn't.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        The best ways to reach me are via
        <a href="https://x.com/mohanrajendran" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
        or
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohan-rajendran-26421335/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>.
        For code, find me on
        <a href="https://github.com/mohanrajendran" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px 120px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.45s ease both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: var(--lh);
    margin-bottom: 1.4em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 2.5em;
    margin-bottom: 0.65em;
  }

  .about-content ul {
    padding-left: 1.5em;
    margin-bottom: 1.4em;
  }

  .about-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    main { padding: 40px 18px 80px; }
  }
</style>
